Eddie Spears https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eddie_Spears 0 Edward "Eddie" Spears (born November 29, 1982) is a Native American actor. He is a member of the Kul Wicasa Oyate Lakota (often called "Sioux") Lower Brulé Sioux Tribe of South Dakota. Edward_"_Eddie_"_Spears ( born November_29_,_1982 ) is a_Native_American_actor .
